column2: IDEA-199485: org.gradle.api.Incubating in Unstable API Inspection

column3:
This is the Gradle Incubating API:
https://docs.gradle.org/current/javadoc/org/gradle/api/Incubating.html
I think it would be valuable for plugin developers and build developers to know when they are using Gradle API's annotated with Incubating.
@vladsoroka Do you need any additional information from me?
Have you submitted a contributor license agreement? If not, please follow the steps described at http://www.jetbrains.com/agreements/cla/ to sign it.
@vladsoroka We've received the CLA from Jonathan, everything is fine here.
I see, @JLLeitschuh thanks, the change has been merged uinsg the following commit f0be733
